column5: two guys came back from fishing in the kawarthas... the first guy was preparing his catch, while the second was cleaning his stuff.  the second guy yells across the field to the first "what are you making?" the first guy answers "well, I am making a crappie soup" the second guy, enraged, yells back and says "stop everything you are doing! don't make a crappie soup- I make the bass soup ever"
Let the Cabin Fever Begin. Lol
